# 📁 Google Drive Automation

## 📖 Overview

Google Drive Automation is an n8n workflow designed to automate file organization and management within Google Drive.

The workflow reduces manual effort by automatically processing uploaded files and organizing them into predefined folders based on business rules.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Automatically monitors Google Drive for new files
- Organizes files into predefined folders
- Supports Google Drive API integration
- Fully automated using n8n workflows
- Easy to customize for different folder structures

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- n8n
- Google Drive API
- Webhooks
- OAuth2 Authentication

---

## ⚙️ Workflow

```text
Trigger
    │
    ▼
Detect New File
    │
    ▼
Evaluate Rules
    │
    ▼
Move File
    │
    ▼
Success Response
```

---

## 📂 Use Cases

- Automatic document organization
- Business document management
- Shared Drive organization
- Team collaboration
- Personal cloud storage automation

